      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-let-000      thru inc-rec-let-999        .
           if        w-exe-flg-brk        not  = spaces
                     go to exe-exp-rsd-800.
       exe-exp-rsd-550.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
