      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-scr-000      thru inc-rec-scr-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-zbb-620.
       exe-exp-zbb-640.
       exe-exp-zbb-690.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
