      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scansione                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
       exe-exp-zso-620.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-001        >    5
                     go to exe-exp-zso-628.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
